Uhm.. It seems this is your first time in Florensia.
Well, I will show how to do the basic things first. Please follow my instructions carefully, so that you can expand the saint's areas of influence.

First of all, to find out how to use weapons, please click the inventory menu box on the right hand side. It is the bag-shaped icon. Alternatively, you can press the l key on the keyboard.

Is the inventory menu box open? Now, drag the mouse to [Tutorial Kiriard] and right-click. You will see the [Tutorial Kiriard] is being loaded on your hand. You can follow the same steps to load [Tutorial Dagger].

If you want to change weapons during the combat, you can press R, or F1, F2, or F3 key on your keyboard.

